overview: The user requested a comprehensive browser-based test of the sleep
  questionnaire application. The agent started by navigating the main
  questionnaire flow, attempting to test form validation. To expedite testing,
  it utilized a developer "Pre-fill & Jump to Report" button to quickly reach
  and test the report generation and PDF download functionality, which worked
  successfully. Subsequently, the agent tested the admin dashboard login,
  verifying that it was protected and that error handling for incorrect
  passwords functioned as expected. A key finding was an issue where alerts on
  the introductory section of the questionnaire were unexpectedly preventing
  navigation to subsequent sections, indicating a potential bug in the form's
  validation or navigation logic.
